{"tid":791754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(高鐵留比你玩) Uber空巴等傳參與日本空中汽車計劃","createTime":"2018-08-24T05:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T05:39:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10ba2af6d77a4cf958a478f17df3dddaf5d84036","tid":791754,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"召車軟件商Uber、飛機製造商空中巴士據報參與日本政府牽頭的「空中汽車」(Flying-Car)項目。<br />\n<br />\n外電引述知情人士透露，日本正開發飛行汽車計劃，參與計劃的包括Uber及空巴等，預計在未來10年為日本推出空中汽車。<br />\n<br />\n計劃的參與者還包括波音公司、豐田汽車、ANA Holdings、日本航空、NEC等約20家企業，有關代表將於本月29日進行會議。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士稱，日本希望率先為此新興航空業制定規則，因政策制定者認為，目前的航空法規大多由歐洲和美國制定。<br />\n<br />\nUber發言人證實參與計劃，但拒絕進一步置評。波音公司、豐田汽車、ANA Holdings、日本航空、NEC等均拒絕評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1925704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1925704&d=EBmLkVgh7RFuXiCufHaeEf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c54d0eab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1925704</a>"},{"pid":"3a0cb8b275d2ebc8f4975a25e8515eb2cc5ec0f7","tid":791754,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實有冇野保障返下面啲人安全"},{"pid":"8c8f2a8bc1da975db3e74a3fd0651ba13b81279e","tid":791754,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a0cb8b275d2ebc8f4975a25e8515eb2cc5ec0f7","tid":791754,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實有冇野保障返下面啲人安全"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"有冇見過飛機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30a6b7552acd026ac114b39127254c1221884ab","tid":791754,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c8f2a8bc1da975db3e74a3fd0651ba13b81279e","tid":791754,"u